      <title>香港金牌得主因亲中论文风波而退役</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/hong-kong-olympic-champion-retires-amid-debate-over-thesis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港奥运会金牌得主孔咏梅表示，她将退出击剑生涯。此前几天，她因明显支持北京镇压香港民主运动而引发争议，凸显了这个亚洲金融中心的政治紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/hong-kong-olympic-champion-retires-amid-debate-over-thesis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:33:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗称将惩罚以色列但希望避免全面战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/iran-says-it-aims-to-reestablish-deterrence-against-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗表示希望避免与以色列爆发全面战争，尽管它威胁要对上周哈马斯领导人在伊朗首都被暗杀一事进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/iran-says-it-aims-to-reestablish-deterrence-against-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:02:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国抗议者游行到达卡，公然反抗总理哈西娜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/bangladesh-protesters-prepare-to-march-to-dhaka-defying-curfew</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，孟加拉国以学生为首的抗议者游行至首都达卡，向总理谢赫·哈西娜施压，要求其辞职，并无视宵禁，而陆军总司令正准备向全国发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/bangladesh-protesters-prepare-to-march-to-dhaka-defying-curfew</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 04:40:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚十年来首次提高恐怖威胁等级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/australia-raises-terror-threat-level-as-radicalization-spreads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于情报界对网络极端主义和以色列与哈马斯战争引发的社区动荡的担忧日益加剧，澳大利亚自 2014 年以来首次提高了该国的恐怖主义威胁等级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/australia-raises-terror-threat-level-as-radicalization-spreads</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 02:52:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜在边境部署数百个新型导弹发射器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/north-korea-deploys-hundreds-of-new-missile-launchers-at-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜表示，已部署 250 辆新型机动弹道导弹发射器，可对韩国和美国在朝鲜的基地实施核打击，这是朝鲜在领导人金正恩领导下最大规模的火箭实力展示之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/north-korea-deploys-hundreds-of-new-missile-launchers-at-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 02:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国爆发骚乱后斯塔默召开紧急会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/starmer-calls-emergency-meeting-after-riots-flare-across-britain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默召开紧急安全会议，试图平息震惊英国各地社区的反移民抗议活动，这些抗议活动有可能使刚刚成立一个月的政府陷入两极分化的文化争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/starmer-calls-emergency-meeting-after-riots-flare-across-britain</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国敦促加沙停火，以色列准备应对伊朗袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/israel-braces-for-attack-from-iran-as-us-urges-gaza-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国向加沙地带派遣防御增援部队并敦促达成停火协议之际，以色列做好了应对伊朗和当地民兵可能发动的袭击的准备，以报复真主党和哈马斯官员遭暗杀事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/israel-braces-for-attack-from-iran-as-us-urges-gaza-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 16:38:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿联酋通过援助加沙和加强与以色列的关系展现外交影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/uae-shows-regional-diplomatic-sway-with-gaza-aid-ties-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布扎比的影子已经来到了阿里什，这是一座位于西奈半岛北部的小城市，距离加沙约 50 公里。这个沿海城市曾经很少有外人来访，但现在却挤满了身穿工装裤和米色背心、印有阿联酋国旗的阿联酋志愿者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/uae-shows-regional-diplomatic-sway-with-gaza-aid-ties-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>疑似胡塞导弹袭击集装箱船 两周内首次遇袭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/suspected-missile-attack-by-yemen-s-houthi-rebels-hits-container-ship-in-first-attack-in-2-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜，阿拉伯联合酋长国（美联社）——当局周日称，也门胡塞叛军发动的导弹袭击击中了一艘穿越亚丁湾的悬挂利比里亚国旗的集装箱船，这是自以色列空袭以来该组织首次发动袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/suspected-missile-attack-by-yemen-s-houthi-rebels-hits-container-ship-in-first-attack-in-2-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 01:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果和卢旺达关系为何如此糟糕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/why-relations-between-congo-and-rwanda-are-so-toxic-quicktake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国东部是非洲最动荡的地区之一，暴力事件导致 700 多万人流离失所，人们担心冲突会加剧。总统费利克斯·齐塞克迪指责卢旺达总统保罗·卡加梅支持一个名为 M23 的叛乱组织。卡加梅否认了这一指控，并反驳说齐塞克迪无法控制自己国家的局势，这对卢旺达构成了安全风险。2024 年初，随着]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/why-relations-between-congo-and-rwanda-are-so-toxic-quicktake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 08:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
